name: Ancient woman (4)
description:
The story of my paintings is based on archetypes of women and geometric symbols, animals, plants and various colors that are related to the human subconscious. When these images become self-aware, they show a different appearance and behavioral characteristics and highlight cultural and historical concepts. As a result, human beings try to achieve their desires through allegorical and symbolic rituals in order to understand the secrets of self-knowledge.
size 50 .70 cm - resolution 300 dpi
